alität! \nJe nach   Kochgewohnheiten   und   Saison   kann ein  Ernteanteil  einen 1-2  Personen  Haushalt mit \nGemüse versorgen. \nDein Gemüse holst du wöchentlich frisch ab im Depot  am \nTempelhof, in Crailsheim oder in Feuchtwangen.  Weitere Abholstellen sind möglich, wenn sich genug Mitglieder zusammentun.\nWir  legen  besonderen  Wert  auf  Humusaufbau, Förderung  der  Artenvielfalt  und  des  Bodenlebens. Unnötige  Verpackung  und  lange  Transportwege fallen weg!","createdAt":"2018-04-20T12:31:18.074Z","updatedAt":"2021-03-09T10:16:25.604Z","country":"DEU","state":"Baden-Württemberg","postalcode":"74594","products":[{"id":"7","category":"animal_products","name":"eggs","type":"Product","link":"/products/7"},{"id":"1","category":"vegetable_products","name":"vegetables","type":"Product","link":"/products/1"},{"id":"5","category":"vegetable_products","name":"bread_and_pastries","type":"Product","link":"/products/5"},{"id":"6","category":"vegetable_products","name":"spices","type":"Product","link":"/products/6"},{"id":"8","category":"animal_products","name":"meat","type":"Product","link":"/products/8"},{"id":"13","category":"animal_products","name":"honey","type":"Product","link":"/products/13"},{"id":"14","category":"beverages","name":"juice","type":"Product","link":"/products/14"},{"id":"2","category":"vegetable_products","name":"fruits","type":"Product","link":"/products/2"},{"id":"4","category":"vegetable_products","name":"cereals","type":"Product","link":"/products/4"}],"badges":[{"id":"1","name":"Netzwerk Solidarische Landwirtschaft e.V.","category":"associations","url":"https://www.solidarische-landwirtschaft.org/","logo":"http://map.ernte-teilen.org/assets/netzwerk_solidarische_landwirtschaft.svg","type":"Badge","link":"/badges/1"}],"depots":{"type":"FeatureCollection","features":[]},"type":"Farm","link":"/farms/198"}}